NAME: Date
DESC: Generates a custom formatted date/datetime/time between two dates.
dFormat: Day of the month without leading zeros
doFormat: Day of the month with suffix
ddFormat: Day of the month with leading zeros
EEEEEFormatExample: M, T, W, T, F, S, S
EEEEEEFormatExample: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Su, Sa
helpIntro: This data type randomly generates a formatted date between two dates. See the table below for a list of viable formatting rules. These are taken from the date-fns date formatting options. Use the example dropdown to select from standard date formats.
endDateEarlierThanStartDate: The end date should be later than the start date
invalidDateFormat: Ungültiges Format. Klicken Sie auf das Zeilenhilfesymbol, um die verfügbaren Formatierungsoptionen anzuzeigen.
